race.comment: LADY JULIETTE (2) was in the minors two back (16.09) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 7th. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Can bounce back. FOSSIL BLUFF (1) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten a head (19.59) behind Lizzy Milici at Hobart. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Can measure up. MAKE IT POP (8) looks close to another win after finishing second from Box 6 last time (16.27) at this track. Boasts a strong record from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from six starts. Expected to be in the finish again. POLLINATOR KEN (4) warrants respect following a recent placing in a tight finish.
